1.7
log
@edma attaches to fdt now
@
text
@.\" $OpenBSD: omap.4,v 1.6 2016/08/11 04:33:06 jsg Exp $
.\" Copyright (c) 2014 Sylvestre Gallon <syl@@openbsd.org>
